PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS establishing the rules for the employer source deduction tables for the period July 1, 1992 to December 31, 1992, reflecting changes in the provincial income tax rate for individuals resident in the provinces of Newfoundland, Ontario, Alberta and British-Columbia and reflecting the annualized effect of the decrease in the federal surtax from 5% to 4% for the 1992 taxation year.
